<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Créer un compte — AgriSense 360</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,500;9..144,700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        :root {
            --g5: #4caf50; --g7: #2e7d32;
            --panel: #1e2d3d;
            --panel-light: #263545;
            --border-inp: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
            --text: #f0f4f8;
            --muted: #8fa4b8;
        }
        html, body { height: 100%; overflow: hidden; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; }

        .split { display: flex; width: 100vw; height: 100vh; }

        /* ── Left dark panel ── */
        .left {
            width: 48%;
            background: var(--panel);
            display: flex; flex-direction: column;
            padding: 32px 52px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            position: relative;
        }

        .left::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(76,175,80,.07) 0%, transparent 60%),
                        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 10%, rgba(46,125,50,.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 32px; position: relative; }
        .brand-icon { width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--g5); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .brand-icon svg { width: 26px; height: 26px; fill: #fff; }
        .brand-name { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.1; }
        .brand-sub  { font-size: .72rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }

        .form-area { position: relative; }

        h1 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 6px; }
        .sub { font-size: .86rem; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 24px; }

        /* Fields */
        .field-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
        .field-label { display: block; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 7px; letter-spacing: .03em; }
        .hint { font-size: .7rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.3); margin-top: 4px; display: block; }

        .inp-wrap { position: relative; }
        .inp-icon { position: absolute; left: 14px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); width: 15px; height: 15px; color: var(--muted); pointer-events: none; }
        .inp-icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; }

        .inp {
            width: 100%; padding: 12px 14px 12px 42px;
            background: var(--panel-light);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-inp);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: .88rem; color: var(--text); outline: none;
            transition: border-color .18s, box-shadow .18s;
        }
        .inp::placeholder { color: rgba(255,255,255,.2); }
        .inp:focus { border-color: var(--g5); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(76,175,80,.15); }

        /* Role */
        .role-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 10px; }
        .role-opt input { display: none; }
        .role-opt label {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            padding: 11px 14px;
            background: var(--panel-light);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-inp);
            border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer;
            font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--muted);
            transition: all .18s;
        }
        .role-opt label:hover { border-color: var(--g5); color: var(--text); }
        .role-opt input:checked + label { border-color: var(--g5); color: var(--g5); background: rgba(76,175,80,.1); }
        .role-icon svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: currentColor; fill: none; }

        /* Section sep */
        .sep { display: block; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .09em; color: var(--muted); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); padding-top: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

        /* Submit */
        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%; padding: 14px;
            background: var(--g5); color: #fff;
            border: none; border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 700; font-size: .95rem;
            cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px;
            transition: background .18s, transform .12s;
            margin-top: 6px; margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .btn-submit:hover { background: var(--g7); transform: translateY(-1px); }

        /* Footer */
        .form-footer { text-align: center; font-size: .78rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; }
        .form-footer a { color: var(--g5); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .copyright { text-align: center; font-size: .72rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.18); margin-top: 20px; }

        /* Divider */
        .divider { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 14px; font-size: .78rem; color: var(--muted); margin: 14px 0; }
        .divider::before, .divider::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.1); }

        /* Social */
        .social-btn {
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 10px;
            width: 100%; padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600; font-size: .86rem;
            cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none;
            transition: opacity .18s; margin-bottom: 8px; border: none;
        }
        .social-btn svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .social-btn:hover { opacity: .88; }
        .btn-google   { background: #fff; color: #1a1a1a; }
        .btn-facebook { background: #1877f2; color: #fff; }
        .btn-apple    { background: #111; color: #fff; }

        /* Alerts */
        .alert-error   { background: rgba(220,38,38,.14); border: 1px solid rgba(220,38,38,.28); color: #fca5a5; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: .83rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
        .alert-success { background: rgba(76,175,80,.14); border: 1px solid rgba(76,175,80,.28); color: #86efac; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: .83rem; margin-bottom: 14px; font-weight: 600; }

        /* ── Right photo ── */
        .right { flex: 1; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .right img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
        .right-overlay {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(10,20,15,.78) 0%, rgba(10,20,15,.12) 50%, transparent 100%);
        }
        .right-caption { position: absolute; bottom: 48px; left: 44px; right: 44px; }
        .right-caption h2 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 2.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.25; }
        .right-caption p  { font-size: .9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 340px; }

        /* features pills */
        .features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; position: absolute; top: 44px; left: 44px; right: 44px; }
        .feat-pill {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);
            border-radius: 50px; padding: 9px 16px;
            font-size: .82rem; color: #fff; font-weight: 500;
            width: fit-content;
        }
        .feat-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--g5); flex-shrink: 0; }

        .help-bubble {
            position: absolute; bottom: 32px; right: 32px;
            width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.18); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: #fff; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="split">

    <!-- ── Left: form ── -->
    <div class="left">
        <div class="brand">
            <div class="brand-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 19.72L5.71 21l1-1.29A4.49 4.49 0 008 20c4 0 4-2 8-2s4 2 8 2v-2c-4 0-4-2-8-2-1.33 0-2.31.15-3.14.37C14 11.54 16 8.36 17 8z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div class="brand-name">AgriSense 360</div>
                <div class="brand-sub">Agriculture Intelligente</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-area">
            <h1>Créer un compte</h1>
            <p class="sub">Rejoignez AgriSense et gérez votre exploitation intelligemment</p>

            {% if error %}
                <div class="alert-error">⚠ {{ error }}</div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if success %}
                <div class="alert-success">✓ {{ success }}</div>
            {% endif %}

            <form method="post" data-validate="register" novalidate>
                <div class="field-group">
                    <label class="field-label">Nom complet</label>
                    <div class="inp-wrap">
                        <span class="inp-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 20c1.5-3 10.5-3 12 0"/></svg></span>
                        <input type="text" name="name" class="inp" placeholder="Ex : Ahmed Ben Ali"
                               value="{{ app.request.request.get('name') }}" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="field-group">
                    <label class="field-label">Adresse email</label>
                    <div class="inp-wrap">
                        <span class="inp-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg></span>
                        <input type="email" name="email" class="inp" placeholder="votreemail@example.com"
                               value="{{ app.request.request.get('email') }}" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="field-group">
                    <label class="field-label">Téléphone <span style="opacity:.5;">(optionnel)</span></label>
                    <div class="inp-wrap">
                        <span class="inp-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2A19.79 19.79 0 0 1 11.82 19 19.45 19.45 0 0 1 4 11.18a2 2 0 0 1 2-2.18h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L10.09 16a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 24 22z"/></svg></span>
                        <input type="tel" name="phone" class="inp" placeholder="Ex : 55 123 456"
                               value="{{ app.request.request.get('phone') }}">
                    </div>
                    <span class="hint">Format tunisien : 8 chiffres commençant par 2, 4, 5, 7 ou 9</span>
                </div>

                <div class="field-group">
                    <label class="field-label">Je suis un(e)...</label>
                    <div class="role-grid">
                        <div class="role-opt">
                            <input type="radio" name="role" id="r_gerant" value="ROLE_GERANT"
                                {{ app.request.request.get('role', 'ROLE_GERANT') != 'ROLE_OUVRIER' ? 'checked' : '' }}>
                            <label for="r_gerant">
                                <span class="role-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 20c1.5-3 10.5-3 12 0"/></svg></span>
                                Gérant
                            </label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="role-opt">
                            <input type="radio" name="role" id="r_ouvrier" value="ROLE_OUVRIER"
                                {{ app.request.request.get('role') == 'ROLE_OUVRIER' ? 'checked' : '' }}>
                            <label for="r_ouvrier">
                                <span class="role-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M7 8h10"/><path d="M6 12h12"/><path d="M8 16h8"/></svg></span>
                                Ouvrier
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <span class="sep">Mot de passe</span>

                <div class="field-group">
                    <label class="field-label">Mot de passe</label>
                    <div class="inp-wrap">
                        <span class="inp-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></span>
                        <input type="password" name="password" class="inp" id="pwd"
                               placeholder="Minimum 8 caractères" required>
                    </div>
                    <div id="pwd-strength"></div>
                    <span class="hint">Doit contenir majuscule, minuscule, chiffre et caractère spécial</span>
                </div>

                <div class="field-group">
                    <label class="field-label">Confirmer le mot de passe</label>
                    <div class="inp-wrap">
                        <span class="inp-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></span>
                        <input type="password" name="confirm_password" class="inp"
                               placeholder="Répéter le mot de passe" required>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Créer mon compte →</button>
            </form>

            <div class="divider">OU</div>

            <a href="#" class="social-btn btn-google">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path fill="#4285F4" d="M22.56 12.25c0-.78-.07-1.53-.2-2.25H12v4.26h5.92c-.26 1.37-1.04 2.53-2.21 3.31v2.77h3.57c2.08-1.92 3.28-4.74 3.28-8.09z"/><path fill="#34A853" d="M12 23c2.97 0 5.46-.98 7.28-2.66l-3.57-2.77c-.98.66-2.23 1.06-3.71 1.06-2.86 0-5.29-1.93-6.16-4.53H2.18v2.84C3.99 20.53 7.7 23 12 23z"/><path fill="#FBBC05" d="M5.84 14.09c-.22-.66-.35-1.36-.35-2.09s.13-1.43.35-2.09V7.07H2.18C1.43 8.55 1 10.22 1 12s.43 3.45 1.18 4.93l3.66-2.84z"/><path fill="#EA4335" d="M12 5.38c1.62 0 3.06.56 4.21 1.64l3.15-3.15C17.45 2.09 14.97 1 12 1 7.7 1 3.99 3.47 2.18 7.07l3.66 2.84c.87-2.6 3.3-4.53 6.16-4.53z"/></svg>
                Continuer avec Google
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="social-btn btn-facebook">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#fff"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/></svg>
                Continuer avec Facebook
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="social-btn btn-apple">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#fff"><path d="M12.152 6.896c-.948 0-2.415-1.078-3.96-1.04-2.04.027-3.91 1.183-4.961 3.014-2.117 3.675-.546 9.103 1.519 12.09 1.013 1.454 2.208 3.09 3.792 3.039 1.52-.065 2.09-.987 3.935-.987 1.831 0 2.35.987 3.96.948 1.637-.026 2.676-1.48 3.676-2.948 1.156-1.688 1.636-3.325 1.662-3.415-.039-.013-3.182-1.221-3.22-4.857-.026-3.04 2.48-4.494 2.597-4.559-1.429-2.09-3.623-2.324-4.39-2.376-2-.156-3.675 1.09-4.61 1.09z"/><path d="M15.53 3.83c.843-1.012 1.4-2.427 1.245-3.83-1.207.052-2.662.805-3.532 1.818-.78.896-1.454 2.338-1.273 3.714 1.338.104 2.715-.688 3.559-1.701z"/></svg>
                Continuer avec Apple
            </a>

            <div class="form-footer">
                <p>Déjà un compte ? <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}">Se connecter</a></p>
            </div>
            <p class="copyright">© 2024 AgriSense 360. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Right: photo ── -->
    <div class="right">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466692476868-aef1dfb1e735?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=85"
             alt="Champs de cultures">
        <div class="right-overlay"></div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feat-pill"><span class="feat-dot"></span> Surveillance en temps réel · 148 capteurs actifs</div>
            <div class="feat-pill"><span class="feat-dot"></span> Alertes IA précoces · 4.8x plus rapide</div>
            <div class="feat-pill"><span class="feat-dot"></span> Rendement optimisé · 98% de performance</div>
        </div>

        <div class="right-caption">
            <h2>Cultivez l'avenir avec l'IA</h2>
            <p>Gérez vos cultures, équipements, animaux et équipes depuis une seule plateforme intelligente</p>
        </div>
        <div class="help-bubble">?</div>
    </div>

</div>
<script src="{{ asset('assets/scripts/validation.js') }}"></script>
</body>
</html>
